body_html:
I am going to mark this as closed unless someone has a report from TF 1.8. No disrespect. It just pops up in my queue and without a repro for TF 1.8 and there are PRs that claim to have possibly fixed the problem it is really stale. If the issue still exists with MKL then we can reopen and then assign to @tatianashp and we can get Intel to address it.

Edit: that indicated we can reopen I meant to include that as an option.
